722C1FA2.Line11.B4310: Skewered like a quill rat. So it goes, eh Deckard?

C4F32199.Line9.B4310: Oh, it’s a shame. (cough) I got mine, just a hair too late. Sneaky devil poked me in the back! (drinks)
